{"tid":1470544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非升級] 全方位和理非抗爭","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:56:55.000Z","uid":291805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"312e858d53b2bb8e9d4d371ed573d01646c754e4","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">目標一致，瞄準極權。</span><br />\n警渣公安臥底黑社會只是模糊焦點的工具。<br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: red;\">打大佬要打頭</span>，唔係打身！！<br />\n前線縱然有錯，全體抗爭者一同道歉，檢討，重新出發，齊上齊落。<br />\n堅持團結，不指責，不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梁天琦格言：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n2. 我們必須反思自己的每一言一行，會使我們離這個目標更近還是更遠。<br />\n3. 懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，更要始終保持理性的思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n共狗再扣港人帽子，打正旗號<span style=\"color: red;\">反恐</span>，企圖殺人如草芥。<br />\n官警黑已凌駕法治，且得到邪惡極權背書。<br />\n勇武正面臨<span style=\"color: red;\">前所未有的生命威脅</span>，再正面交鋒相信只信落得慘淡收場，必須由<span style=\"color: red;\">地上轉為地下</span>。　學另一位巴打話齋，be water已經唔夠，要<span style=\"color: red;\">be air</span>!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1454288/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1454288/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n95%和理非都錫身，郁啲就散水，返屋企睇直播，變身民意撚，<span style=\"color: red;\">對運動唔會有任何幫助</span>。<br />\n前線搵命搏，深怕一撤就輸，某程度上係因為<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非一盤散沙，做唔到實事</span>。<br />\n和理非們，請搵返6.16 <span style=\"color: red;\">200萬人一條心</span>果一股氣勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">全面step up</span>，救救前線，攞返主動權！！　長期抗戰！！！　唔Ｌ可以停，重覆再重覆，要<span style=\"color: red;\">培養成習慣</span>！！<br />\n<br />\n和理非只要<span style=\"color: red;\">夠齊心</span>，其實有好多野可以做！！<br />\n中美貿易戰，大好時機，伸多佢一腳！！<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">全民走資，轉玩美股</span> - 商家佬已走左唔少，而家輪到民間。 <span style=\"color: red;\">開離岸戶口</span>，將大部份身家<span style=\"color: red;\">抽離本港銀行體系</span>，保障自己，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡賣中港股，轉玩美股</span>，大把野揀，唔洗買垃圾，期權股票乜都齊，也給港元壓力，挑戰港府外匯儲備。 <span style=\"color: red;\">MPF</span>同時轉歐美組合，唔玩中港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_673858_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_673858_0&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=b7f0a58a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_673858_0&h=8208e64e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_673858_0</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">罷買罷食時間表</span> - 要目標清晰，全世界都知，集中火力，逐一對付<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍底黑底</span>商戶。 建議列出<span style=\"color: red;\">每星期甚至每月的抵制目標名單</span>，包括商場，食肆，連鎖店，品牌和服務，然後加以宣傳和動員，<span style=\"color: red;\">不斷重覆，直至5大訴求獲正面回應</span>。 重點係<span style=\"color: red;\">抵制時間要夠長</span>，先會覺得痛。　先抵制紅色企業，再到本地藍黑企業。　例如，先抵制香港航空，因為國泰俾人揸春袋，局表態，但始終都係港資。　我地目標係要先搞死背後揸佢既惡勢力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制紅媒</span> - CCTVB，所有黨媒黨報等等。 好明顯，9成人買成箱寶礦力自high之後冇左件事。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 繼續轉台！！</span>　屋企，茶餐廳，見親都轉去港台／VIU／有線。　繼續搞鳩佢地既廣告客戶，抵制佢地既商品服務。　商場活動，真真假假，有時出現，有時凶鳩佢地已經夠，場地技術司儀藝人化妝保險一早要安排，樣樣都係錢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1250543/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1250543/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">支持本地直播，講人話既媒體</span> - subscribe立場，蘋果，港台，商台，城寨等等，要金錢上實際支持佢地。<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">本地文宣</span> - target <span style=\"color: red;\">11月24日區選</span>，target<span style=\"color: blue;\">淺藍同中間派[/red]，<span style=\"color: red;\">分區分target audience接收唔同資訊</span>，例如太古城沙田中產多，應該唔少淺黃淺藍。　呢班人先係勝負關鍵，唔好再同黃絲圍爐取暖。 行動上，<span style=\"color: red;\">真係盡量唔好搞到民生(包括機場)</span>，否則中間派支持流失，我地票都冇埋。　記住唔好同呢班人講自由公義講理念，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地唔介意你幫佢爭取埋，但你搞到佢就係大問題。</span> 代入角色，幻想自己係一個自私精，你先會諗到要同佢地講乜。　點出[blue]民建聯</span>作為第一大黨多年來的好事多為，如何作為或不作為，造成今天矛盾仇恨，市面大亂，唔安全，出街隋時俾人拉俾人打，食催淚彈，黑社會橫行警察唔做野，市民恐慌，經濟差，無任何人出嚟承擔，亦無任何對策，淨係盲撐警，甚至撐黑社會。　<span style=\"color: red;\">要將佢地同無恥無能既政府綑綁，同黑社會同黑警綑綁，不斷重提721</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438967/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438967/page/1</a><br />\n另霑叔既智慧分享 - 真正尊重所有人的睇法，權利，<span style=\"color: red;\">冇得夾硬嚟</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKMsOd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKMsOd7.png&h=37ee8d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">向內地人文宣</span> -  禮貌禮貌禮貌，和平和平和平。　落遊客區，香港境內中港碼頭，高鐵站，機場等等，宣傳香港正在發生既事，<span style=\"color: red;\">打溫情牌</span>。　訴說香港人抗爭其實只係延續30年前既北京學運，令內地人產生共鳴感，繼而同情及支持港人，反到<span style=\"color: red;\">上去播種</span>。　有巴打寫呢篇寫得好好 - &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">港抗爭者致大陸同胞書</span>&quot;，相信佢唔介意我地借用廣傳。 另有巴打提出寄信，也可以試。<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/2942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F2942&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=aa677327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/2942</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436202/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436202/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: red;\">交稅不合作。</span>　合法，唔會有late penalty。 每人交多幾蚊，等佢開cheque，退到仆街。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1393880/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1393880/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n8. <span style=\"color: red;\">11.24區會選舉日</span>。 要諗盡方法說服自己藍絲阿爸阿媽，當然係難，但試下<span style=\"color: red;\">動之以情</span>，因為佢地好多都好似信左邪教咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好同佢地講logic</span>。 如果唔得，就諗方法令佢地當日冇辦法喺香港出現投票，早啲安排，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">幫佢地報個玩兩日，飲飲食食既大陸團，雙魚星號乜都好</span>，你請佢地多數會去。<br />\n<br />\n9. <span style=\"color: red;\">人道救援基金損款，聯署，眾籌登報</span>，要多多支持<br />\n<br />\n10. <span style=\"color: red;\">罷工罷課罷市</span> - 必要時再號召，但唔可以時時用。　始終各有各生活壓力，唔可以阻人返工。　要尊重所有人的自由意志！<br />\n<br />\n11. 最後，呼籲各大良心商店，服務，團體，自發<span style=\"color: red;\">謝絕警員及其家屬</span>幫襯或參與。　<span style=\"color: red;\">所有絲打唔好so啲警渣，唔好受佢地溝!!! 鄙視佢地!!! 打擊佢地自信!!! 踩到佢地變地底泥!!! </span> 講完!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同意請大大力推，我地要動員200萬人!!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"852d774130424272743c8e7cafd1d26745eb982f","tid":1470544,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"62a2d3d0a4be78e64cad1ef7e612252e1ad3e9ce","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"自10連推"},{"pid":"b4406e049d3921e15f9e6e009392c21f8ae65069","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"4d5ccce8de5534875dec87d8aa2ab0c0b56523ca","tid":1470544,"uid":303229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e57cb7b8dcb3251c06e4e014ceb6a1934ca81f2f","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"c166f7735c73a430789b142da716ac3e75b0b09d","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f3cc61755104403c646dcb406bf34d952e37ae20","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"78d7e228e1319e43e6cd33f678ab346e470aeda3","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5c201bd1a2fa747a97adf5b2b7241b063533754a","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0f719dbc5761b21dde17551cee09c1b3c3af7e40","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"17a4069538dca997f3070953c238812d88e41f51","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"39d61574b124c0843779fb83d46ca9f900471009","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d578d1043225977b48db65765fe9ed4994e71c14","tid":1470544,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dbec0c89244cb7fe2ae18090424e4aafa169a92","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"5846844f3580d47a914336bf6bc9da298f23bf45","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524b34416a6c79381b20c975d3481e1b5d7cb679","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72522c7b8ccc245295b4748bc392fc6174a12d9","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a2a33c759733517c6b4d02b0c7b70512d64ffe","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47a850b630727c22eed5f5f1e8617e95b755b67","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72edc14532e409078a3261c1c3eb968897ad4487","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d749373f687b3306aa1c995d1bba3bd67256291a","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bcc9f1a9247697a65f0713ce1319105f66aec87","tid":1470544,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392daf57e995ae8d177269275f27f0fb6b9b8582","tid":1470544,"uid":262522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ec2344fbc7b49adf51f866f3c6c797eef21874","tid":1470544,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"連登改咗P牌冇得俾like<br />\n咁我哋呢啲一世P牌想支持唯有推吓post"}]}